---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.tsx'
import '../index.css'
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - PhyloGuessr">
  <div class="game">
    <Header client:load />
    <div class="about-page">
      <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p><em>Last updated: March 7, 2026</em></p>

      <h3>Analytics</h3>
      <p>We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use PhyloGuessr. Google Analytics collects information such as how often you visit, what pages you view, and your approximate location. This data is aggregated and anonymous. Google Analytics places cookies on your browser to identify you as a unique visitor. For more details, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h3>Account data</h3>
      <p>If you choose to log in, we use Firebase Authentication to manage your account. We store your display name and a user identifier to show you as an online player. Your game history is stored locally in your browser and is not sent to our servers.</p>
      <p>We use Firebase to track presence data (e.g. how many people are currently online). Logged-in users appear by display name; this data is not shared beyond the online count shown in the app.</p>

      <h3>Cookies</h3>
      <p>We use cookies for Google Analytics (as described above) and to keep you logged in if you have an account.</p>

      <h3>Third-party services</h3>
      <p>We rely on Google Analytics and Firebase (both Google services). Their use of your data is governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h3>Changes</h3>
      <p>If we change this policy, we'll update the date at the top of this page.</p>

      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:colin.diesh@gmail.com">colin.diesh@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
